For lung cancer, the recommended daily dose of Tarceva is 150 mg.
Tarceva is taken at least one hour before or two hours after food.
If needed (for example because of side effects), the dose may be reduced in 50 mg steps.
Treatment of pancreatic cancer should be re-assessed after 4 to 8 weeks if no rash has developed.
Tarceva is not recommended for use in patients with severe liver or kidney disease.
